description.details: The Overlap Hoodie from Icecream. This men's pullover hoodie features a screen print on the chest with a kangaroo pouch pocket at the belly and an adjustable hood with drawstrings. This hoodie comes with a button-on removeable facemask that attaches to the inside of the hood.

Designed in partnership with Born x Raised, this edition of Lira is conceived as a celebration of community and creativity. Rooted in authentic Angeleno culture, over the last decade, Born x Raised has become recognised for its unique creative approach that celebrates the city’s history and diverse local identity. This version of Lira, an angular and thick acetate shape, features a rich Havana acetate with exclusive gold inscriptions on the temples and on the top of the rims, topped off with a unique a metal gold ring encasing the lenses. This is one of the last collaborations that Spanto co-designed. Spanto forever.
